{"tid":1482313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多名刀手駱克道伏擊 4酒吧職員受傷","createTime":"2019-08-18T05:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T05:07:18.000Z","uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"930b95a6508e93a27504a7871824842b834271ba","tid":1482313,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:04:35.000Z","msg":"中午12時許，灣仔駱克道88號一間酒吧發生斬人血案，包括刀手在內涉及十多人，消息指有至少6名戴上黑色口罩，持刀及鐵通等武器的兇徒，在一間酒吧門外施襲，至少4名酒吧職員受傷，其中1人頭部重傷，刀手逞兇後即時四散。警方及救護員趕到現場，將傷者送院治理，現場有一輛車窗破碎的私家車被警方扣查，警方正調查事件起因，暫時無人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190818/59945092\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190818%2F59945092&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPPzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=d7161306\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190818%2F59945092&h=504fcf45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190818/59945092</a><br />\n<br />\n小心保護身邊既手足 唔好落單 2點維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35351194aaa0449528fee12e28edf2723a13ce59","tid":1482313,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:05:00.000Z","msg":"維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb8602ae38d9e7138d21acc3f45f0a51185716a","tid":1482313,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:05:10.000Z","msg":"維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac566dac0923a1da18ade29cd3e6cd7bb5d3921a","tid":1482313,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"黑警無權進入私人地方！請廣傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1482232